title: US: Russia, Iran moving toward full defense ‘partnership’
description: The Biden administration is accusing Russia of moving to provide advanced military assistance to Iran, including air defense systems, helicopters and fighter jets

title: Judge declines DOJ request to hold Trump team in contempt over classified documents
description: A federal judge has declined a DOJ request to hold Trump's team in contempt over classified documents.

title: Squirrel shooter arrested after bullet breaks child's window
description: A 76-year-old Minnesota man is facing criminal charges because he was shooting at a squirrel and a bullet went through a child’s bedroom window in a neighboring home

title: Rioter who assaulted cops at Capitol gets 5 years in prison
description: A Tennessee man who authorities say came to Washington ahead of the Jan. 6, 2021, riot ready for violence in a car full of weapons and assaulted officers who were trying to defend the Capitol has been sentenced to more than five years behind bars

title: WATCH:  Rare bird found inside Hawaii Volcanoes National Park
description: The akeake, or band-rumped storm petrel, are heard but rarely seen.

title: More funds recovered for victims of Bernie Madoff
description: This is the 14th distribution to victims of Madoff’s Ponzi scheme.

title: WATCH:  This girl’s face is pure joy when she finds her family in the crowd
description: Emmy Krow’s mom told "GMA" that her daughter "has spread so much love and joy. It’s so nice to see humanity united in a positive way"

title: How human activity is 'decimating' marine life, according to threatened species list
description: Human activity is wreaking havoc on the state of the oceans around the world -- especially on marine life, according to the updated IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.

title: WATCH:  Cat climbs into Christmas tree to play with ornaments
description: This kitty liked Christmas tree ornaments so much, she became one herself!
